# Local dev overrides
*.local

# Stray Python lockfile: ward ships no Python and denies bare `uv` (cmd/ward/hook.go).
# A uv.lock only ever lands here if a uv-using tool (e.g. pre-commit's Python hook
# envs) drops one in the tree. Never tracked - keep it invisible rather than churn.
uv.lock

# Runtime spec cache fetched by `make lock` / skew checks; never committed (ward#62).
# The committed spec lock is a distinct name (*.swagger.lock.json) and IS tracked.
*.swagger.v1.json
cmd/ward-kdl/main.go

# specverb-gen emits one surface reference beside each Guardfile (the only path
# it knows); the reviewed copies live at docs/ward-kdl.*.guardfile.md. One per
# merged API (ward-kdl.<api>.guardfile.md).
cmd/ward-kdl/ward-kdl.*.guardfile.md
